benak.tomas.crimemonitor.client

Class CrimeListItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • benak.tomas.crimemonitor.client.CrimeListItem

  • public class CrimeListItem
extends java.lang.Object
    CrimeListItem is a class used to logically represent the item in a list of crimes.

    The list of crimes is displayed on the crime list activity page. The list is displayed in a list view using the CrimeListAdapter.

    Author:
    Tom
    See Also:
    CrimeListAdapter, CrimesListActivity
